article_title: Boehner: Bill is ‘victory for common sense’

article_metadata.description: Video on NBCNews.com: House Speaker John Boehner speaks at a rally following the House vote to pass a spending bill that temporary prevents a government shutdown and defunds Obamacare, saying “We had a victory today for the American people, and frankly, we had a victory for common sense.”
article_metadata.title: Boehner: Bill is ‘victory for common sense’
